name: Kiss Nesting Side Tables with Bronze Patina Brass Details
description: The Kiss Nesting side tables by Kifu Paris are both elegant and organic in their unique design. The cream shagreen inlaid piece curves inwards to create the 'kiss' effect. The borders are accentuated by bronze-patina brass. These pieces are designed by Kifu Augousti the daughter of Ria and Yiouri Augousti. Available in other finishes and to purchase separately. Part of the Kiss Capsule. Currently made to order 8-10 weeks. Design SKU reference KST42. Handmade. Antique Natural Shagreen or Shell surface, Bronze-Patina Brass legs.
